temptation is a 1946 american thriller film noir directed by irving pichel starring merle oberon , george brent , charles &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and paul lukas . the film was based on robert smythe hichens 's novel bella donna . the 1923 film bella donna , starring pola negri , which was directed by george fitzmaurice is also based on that novel . other versions were filmed in 1918 and 1935 .